snippet.title: Himawari CATASTROPHE!
snippet.description:
Hack and slash your way through the Garden of the Sun as Tenshi Hinanawi in Himawari CATASTROPHE!

This game was made in a little over a week for Touhou Fan Game Jam 15!

https://crows-nest.itch.io/himawari-catastrophe
https://itch.io/jam/touhou-jam-15
